{
  "stem": "5795.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I pick out a cellophane packet of sweets, on which was written, this is a gift from the Rotary Club Havana, Cuba.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A strange feeling came over me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I-- I can't believe any British Tom is gonna sit down and write a letter of thanks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Here's the letter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Dated the 3rd of December, 1944.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Can I read it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Certainly.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'The president of the Rotary Club of Havana, Cuba.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's my pleasure and privilege to write to you on behalf of the lads of the British of the raiding army, who I've had the honor to serve to express our most grateful thanks and appreciation for the packets of sweets, et cetera, you most graciously sent us.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So far as the sweets, or should it be designated candy, is concerned, there is no need for me to say how delicious they are.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we do most sincerely appreciate the thought behind the gift, for this too, we say thank you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Many of us belong to the various branches of the British Rotary Clubs, which in these times, the purpose of their existence only gains in tremendous significance.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the great battles which are being waged for liberty, freedom, and righteousness for all nations, the international humanitarianism of you aims and objects stand out above all else.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Under the present conditions, we become more and more men of action, and less and less a vociferous verbiage.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "With this thought, allow me to terminate this letter, reiterating our ever gracious thanks to all those grand, warm-hearted people who made possible the distribution of these packets of candy.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
